OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FA mother from Leicestershire is
OL,8,Fbacking calls for the Government to
OL,9,Fformally apologise, after her son was
OL,10,Ftaken away from her 58 years ago at
OL,11,Fjust one-week-old.
OL,13,FSandra Hobson from Hinckley didn't see
OL,14,Fher son Tony for 53 years - she was
OL,15,Freunited with him for the first time
OL,16,Fin 2021, after her son found her on
OL,17,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
