OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FAn estimated 185,000 children were
OL,8,Ftaken from unmarried mothers and
OL,9,Fadopted between 1949 and 1976 in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FWitnesses and victims gave evidence at
OL,13,Fa Parliamentary Education Committee
OL,14,Ftoday, where Children and Families
OL,15,FMinister, Josh MacAlister, said an
OL,16,Fapology for the state's role in
OL,17,Fhistoric forced adoption is being
OL,18,F"actively considered" by the
OL,19,FGovernment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
