FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FA report by the UK Government's Joint
OL,8,FCommittee on Human Rights (JCHR) in
OL,9,F2022 recommended ministers apologise
OL,10,Fto unmarried women who were
OL,11,F"railroaded" into unwanted adoptions.
OL,13,FJosh MacAlister MP today said he
OL,14,Frecognised the urgency with which the
OL,15,Fissue of the state's role in historic
OL,16,Fforced adoption needs to be addressed,
OL,17,Fbut did not commit to a timescale for
OL,18,Fwhen a formal apology might be issued
OL,19,Fby the Government.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FIn 2023, responding to the report, the
OL,8,Fthen-Conservative government said
OL,9,Fwhile it was sorry "on behalf of
OL,10,Fsociety" for the way the women had
OL,11,Fbeen treated, it did not think a
OL,12,Fformal apology appropriate "since the
OL,13,Fstate did not actively support these
OL,14,Fpractices".
OL,16,FThe JCHR at the time said the lack of
OL,17,Fapology was "disappointing".
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@HO]tD@\OUvD@JO]yD@MOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
