PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FMr MacAlister told the Education
OL,8,FCommittee on Tuesday: "The case for an
OL,9,Fapology is powerful, and it is
OL,10,Fsomething that the Government is
OL,11,Factively considering".
OL,26,@pD@WOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
