PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FHe said he accepted "the state had a
OL,8,Frole" in "a practice that went on for
OL,9,Fdecades, forcibly removing children
OL,10,Ffrom these women in homes that were
OL,11,Fsometimes run by the state, enabled
OL,12,Fand overseen by social workers
OL,13,Femployed by the state, and social
OL,14,Fattitudes that were reinforced by
OL,15,Fpractices that carried on for many
OL,16,Fyears".
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@EO]pD@JOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FHe said he understood campaigners'
OL,8,Fcalls for a formal, official
OL,9,FGovernment apology, adding: "That is
OL,10,Fsomething that is being actively
OL,11,Fconsidered, as of now, by the
OL,12,FGovernment."
OL,14,FHe said it would need to be delivered
OL,15,F"by someone senior in Government to
OL,16,Freflect the gravity of what happened".
OL,26,@qD@]OUtD@LO]wD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773220132
OL,3,C'My baby was taken from me': Mum
OL,4,Cdemands apology 58 years after forced
OL,5,Cadoption
OL,7,FMPs were told by campaigners that
OL,8,Falongside an apology more support was
OL,9,Fneeded for mothers and adoptees,
OL,10,Fincluding fast-tracking them for
OL,11,Ftrauma-informed support as well as
OL,12,Fbetter access to their records.
OL,14,FThe Department for Education said
OL,15,Fthat, following concerns raised by the
OL,16,FMAA about difficulties obtaining
OL,17,Fadoption records, the Government is
OL,18,Fboosting funding by #200,000 to help
OL,19,Fsupport those trying to locate records
OL,20,Fand reconnect with their birth
OL,21,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/8
